Package: CellSpectra
Type: Package
Title: Quantifying Changes in Gene Expression Coordination
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Konstantin A. Klötzer, Nancy R. Zhang, Katalin Susztak
Maintainer: Konstantin A. Klötzer <konstantin.kloetzer@gmail.com>
Description: This package enables the quantification of changes in gene
    expression coordination of cellular functions within single-cell RNA-seq
    atlases. It provides tools for comparing query samples to reference data and
    identifying dysregulated pathways at single-sample resolution.
URL: https://github.com/kloetzerka/CellSpectra
BugReports: https://github.com/kloetzerka/CellSpectra/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
